    "text": "def sigma_plus(S):\n return np.log(S + 1)\n\ndef qft_propagator(k, m=1.0): # QFT传播子G(k)\n return 1 / (k**2 + m**2)\n\ndef integrated_G(m=1.0): # ∫ d^k G(k) 示例 (1D简化)\n def integrand(k):\n return qft_propagator(k, m)\n integral, _ = quad(integrand, -np.inf, np.inf)\n return integral / (2 * np.pi) # 归一化\n\ndef phi1(Pi, e, Sigma_plus, alpha=0.1, Delta_sigma=0.2):\n G_int = integrated_G()\n phi = Pi * e * Sigma_plus + alpha * G_int * Delta_sigma # 融合QFT项\n return phi"
