    "text": "\\leq\n\n\\frac{\\langle\n\n\\psi(\\theta)\n\n|\n\nH\n\n|\n\n\\psi(\\theta)\n\n\\rangle}{\\langle\n\n\\psi(\\theta)\n\n|\n\n\\psi(\\theta)\n\n\\rangle}\n\nEmin ≤\n⟨\nψ(θ)\n∣\nψ(θ)\n⟩⟨\nψ(θ)\n∣\nH\n∣\nψ(θ)\n⟩\n\n3.\n优\n化\n循\n环\n：\n\nAI\n\n不\n断\n调\n整\n策\n略\n参\n数\n\nθ\\\ntheta\nθ\n\n（改\n变\n认\n知\n/\n行\n为）\n，\n直\n到\n找\n到\n\nEEE\n\n4.\n\n的\n极\n小\n值。\n这\n就\n是\n给\n用\n户\n的\n**“\n最\n优\n解\n”\n**\n。\n\n第\n五\n节\n：\n进\n阶\n代\n码\n实\n现\n\n(LoongOne_QFT_Engine)\n\n这\n是\n基\n于\n格\n点\nQFT\n和\nVQE\n思\n想\n的\n\nPython\n\n实\n现。\n它\n模\n拟\n了\n一\n个\n场\n在\n“\n龙\n一\n法\n则\n”\n下\n的\n自\n主\n演\n化。\n\ncode Python\ndownloadcontent_copy\nexpand_less\n import numpy as np\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n\nclass LoongOneQFTEngine:\n def __init__(self, size=20, mass=1.0, coupling=0.1, eta_strength=0.2):\n self.N = size\n\nself.m\n\n=\n\nmass\n\n#\n\n惯\n性\n/\n阻\n尼\n\nself.lam\n\n=\n\ncoupling\n\n#\n\n非\n线\n性\n涌\n现\n系\n数\n\n(1+1=3)\n\nself.eta = eta_strength # 遁 一 / 随 机 强 度\n\n#\n\n初\n始\n化\n格\n点\n场\n\n(Phi)\n\n-\n\n代\n表\n空\n间\n中\n各\n点\n的\n正\n性\n值\n\nself.phi = np.random.normal(0, 0.1, (size, size))\n\ndef action(self, phi):\n \"\"\"\n\n计\n算\n格\n点\n行\n动\n量\n\nS_lat\n\nS = Kinetic + Mass + Interaction + LoongOne_Source\n \"\"\"\n\n#\n\n1.\n\n动\n能\n/\n梯\n度\n项\n\n(\n邻\n居\n差\n异\n)\n\n#\n\n使\n用\n\nnp.roll"
