    "text": "# dS/dphi\n laplacian = (np.roll(self.phi, 1, axis=0) + np.roll(self.phi, -1, axis=0) +\n np.roll(self.phi, 1, axis=1) + np.roll(self.phi, -1, axis=1) - 4*self.phi)\n\ngrad_S = -laplacian + self.m**2 * self.phi + self.lam * self.phi**3\n\n#\n\n加\n入\n龙\n一\n随\n机\n力\n\n(Langevin\n\n方\n程\n中\n的\n噪\n声\n)\n\nnoise = np.random.normal(0, np.sqrt(2*learning_rate), self.phi.shape)\n\n#\n\n更\n新\n场\n\n(\n向\n低\n行\n动\n量\n/\n高\n概\n率\n方\n向\n流\n动\n)"
