    "text": "**第3个 Code 单元格（关键公式推导）**\n\nPython\n\n```\nprint(\"【1. Bernoulli 引力等效】\")\nBernoulli = Eq(p + sp.Rational(1,2)*rho_plenum*(v.T*v)[0], symbols('const'))\npprint(Bernoulli)\n\nprint(\"\\n【2. 引力表达式】\")\nGravity_eq = Eq(symbols('F_grav'), -diff(p, symbols('r')))\npprint(Gravity_eq)\n\nprint(\"\\n【3. 粒子质量（涡旋环）】\")\nmass_vortex = Eq(symbols('m'), rho_plenum * Gamma * pi * R_ring**2)\npprint(mass_vortex)\n\nprint(\"\\n【4. Hopfion能量-拓扑荷关系（V12.28核心）】\")\nE_hopf = (1 + lambda_skyrme * H**2) * symbols('E_0')\npprint(E_hopf)\n\nprint(\"\\n【5. Q-ball有效势稳定性条件】\")\nU_eff = Function('U_eff')(Q)\nstability_condition = Eq(diff(U_eff, Q), 0)\npprint(stability_condition)\n\nprint(\"\\n【6. 光波方程（机械激波）】\")\nwave_eq = Eq(diff(p, symbols('t'), 2), c**2 * diff(p, symbols('x'), 2))\npprint(wave_eq)\n```"
