    "text": "**关键伪代码**（V12.28 LongCpotResidenceModel核心）：\n\nPython\n\n```\n # V12.28 HFCD Hopfion数值步进（简化版）\n def hopfion_step(self, phi, dphi, dt, H=1.0, lambda_skyrme=2.5):\n U_prime = (1 + lambda_skyrme * H**2) * (phi - phi**3) + self.cavity_force(phi)\n d2phi = -U_prime - self.gamma * dphi # 阻尼项\n # RK4 更新\n k1 = dphi\n k2 = dphi + 0.5 * dt * d2phi\n # ... (完整RK4省略)\n new_phi = phi + dt * (k1 + 2*k2 + 2*k3 + k4)/6\n new_dphi = dphi + dt * (l1 + 2*l2 + 2*l3 + l4)/6\n # 拓扑荷投影（每100步审计）\n self.H_current = self.compute_hopf_charge(new_phi)\n return new_phi, new_dphi\n ```"
