    "text": "11. API 級能力設計\n11.1 請求結構\n{  \"model\": \"gemini\",  \"mode\": \"refine\",  \"user_goal\": \"...\",  \"input_text\": \"...\",  \"constraints\": {  \"tone\": \"confident\",  \"format\": \"markdown\",  \"max_length\": 2000  },  \"wuxing_os\": {  \"enable_hfcd_diagnosis\": true,  \"enable_q_centered_guard\": true,  \"enable_energy_ledger\": true,  \"enable_stable_ridge_protection\": true  } }\n11.2 響應結構\n{  \"answer\": \"...\",  \"diagnosis\": {  \"Q_core\": \"...\",  \"FailureMode_before\": \"...\",  \"FailureMode_after\": \"...\",  \"Risk_before\": 0.62,  \"Risk_after\": 0.21,  \"StabilityMargin_before\": -0.14,  \"StabilityMargin_after\": 0.38  },  \"ledger\": {  \"primitive_value_count\": 5,  \"duplicate_light_removed\": 3  },  \"repair_trace\": [  \"Q-centered correction\",  \"energy ledger cleanup\",  \"coupling-to-structure conversion\"  ] }\n11.3 產品賣點\n對外可以這樣表達：\n物性論 OS 不是普通 prompt 模板，而是一個基於 HFCD 穩定窗理論的認知穩定中間層。它通過 Q 核錨定、關係腔構建、能量賬本審計、FailureMode 診斷、守恆中心接受門和穩定脊保護機制，提高大語言模型回答的目標一致性、結構穩定性、事實邊界和創造質量。\n\n12. 下一步研究路線\n當前 HFCD 最新正式狀態：\nV11.10c-3Q: stable = 9/36 baseline_stable = 6/36 stable_gain = +3 energy_surplus_overflow = 15 -> 11 stable_preserved = True\n建議路線：\nV11.10c-4..."
